r />\n\t4) Anything you would like to write&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tRanging from countries to individuals, financial predicament is inevitable whenever the unbalance of revenue and expenditure occurs. According to a survey conducted by a distinguished institution, 68 percent of people who suffer from financial predicament is due to the exceeding expenses. However, financial predicament is a tough nut to tackle despite the fact that the methods to overcome it are extremely simple. Unfortunately, increasing income requires efforts whereas reducing expenses gives rise to <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/psychological\" target=\"_blank\">psychological</a> discomfort. All these can teach us a lesson that keep income and cost in balance is extraordinarily significant.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/169349899841/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p810703/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p810703\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733492/\">25个小短句 测试你的英语水平</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p592946/\">推荐！口语入门的经典教材</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p833096/\">深度解读：如何有效学习？如何成为专家？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p834895/\">双语美文：在逆境中学到了人生最重要的一课</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p836750/\">美帝总统辩论开战，神盾局决定支持希拉里？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767739/\">段子手的自白：我是如何从421进化到515的！</